videos.headline: Dennis Smith Jr. with a strong take to the rim early on for NC State

videos.description: Luke Kennard gets the ball and passes to Harry Giles, who drains the shot and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Great pass from Luke Kennard sets up a Harry Giles score

videos.description: Frank Jackson inbounds a pass up to Harry Giles to finish with the dunk for Duke.
videos.headline: Jackson lobs it up to Giles for the dunk

videos.description: While heading back to the bench, Grayson Allen is impeded by NC State's Terry Henderson, who does not want to let Allen by.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen gets tangled up with NC State players on way to bench in loss

videos.description: NC State's Markell Johnson  strips Frank Jackson and dunks on the other end
videos.headline: NC State's Markell Johnson  strips Frank Jackson and dunks on the other end
DUKE VS NCST

videos.description: Grayson Allen gets the ball and drives past the NC State defense for the acrobatic layup to increase Duke's lead.
videos.headline: Allen drives in for the acrobatic layup

videos.description: Dennis Smith Jr. nails a three at the end of the first half
videos.headline: Dennis Smith Jr. nails a three at the end of the first half

videos.description: Duke's Associate Head Coach Jeff Capel says Duke needs to do a better job on Dennis Smith Jr. in the second half
videos.headline: Duke's Associate Head Coach Jeff Capel says Duke needs to do a better job on Dennis Smith Jr. in the second half

videos.description: Dennis Smith Jr. passes off to Abdul-Malik Abu, who finishes with the two-handed dunk for NC State.
videos.headline: Abu slams it home for NC State

videos.description: NC State misses a couple of shots but Ted Kapita is there for the big putback dunk.  He celebrates by hanging onto to the rim and gets called for a technical.
videos.headline: Ted Kapita's big putback dunk ends with a technical foul

videos.description: Jayson Tatum drives past the NC State defense and finishes with a one-handed dunk to give Duke back the lead.
videos.headline: Tatum drives in for the one-handed jam

videos.description: Matt Jones steals the ball away and lobs a pass up to Frank Jackson, who finishes with the dunk.
videos.headline: Frank Jackson goes flying to catch and slam an alley oop

videos.description: Awesome crossover creates space for Jayson Tatum to drive and score
videos.headline: Awesome crossover creates space for Jayson Tatum to drive and score

videos.description: Great spin move and layup from Dennis Smith Jr.
videos.headline: Great spin move and layup from Dennis Smith Jr.
Abu throws it down with authority for NC State

videos.description: Dennis Smith Jr. lobs a pass up to Abdul-Malik Abu, who capitalizes by dunking it down.
videos.headline: Abu dunks it again for NC State

videos.description: NC State coach Mark Gottfried breaks down his team's huge 84-82 win over Duke.
videos.headline: NC State head coach Mark Gottfried on his team's huge 84-82 win over Duke

videos.description: NC State misses a free throw and Jayson Tatum grabs the rebound for Duke. Tatum taking it down the court, but Dennis Smith Jr. steals it away and finishes with a dunk that would not count on the other end as NC State defeats Duke 84-82.
videos.headline: Duke turns it over on final possession to give NC State win

videos.description: Dennis Smith Jr. breaks down the exciting final minute of NC State's win over Duke and playing against childhood friends Jayson Tatum and Harry Giles.
videos.headline: Smith Jr. wants every game to be like NC State's win over Duke
